last_episode_to_air.name: Am I the Ice Hole? Adventure
last_episode_to_air.overview: Honeybee and Beef bond on an ice fishing trip and try to find a compromise between quiet fishing and fun games.

name: The Great North
overview: Follow the Alaskan adventures of the Tobin family as a single dad does his best to keep his weird bunch of kids close, especially as the artistic dreams of his only daughter lead her away from the family fishing boat and into the glamorous world of the local mall.

episodes.name: Sexi Moose Adventure
episodes.overview: While the children's mother is not in the picture, Judy seeks guidance from her new boss, Alyson, and her imaginary friend, Alanis Morissette, who appears to her in the Northern Lights. The family's plans to celebrate Judy's 16th birthday on the family fishing boat go awry after a moose breaks into the Tobin's home.

episodes.name: Feast of Not People Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy is worried that she and Ham are growing apart when she discovers he's been keeping a secret from her. The rest of the family participates in a town festival.

episodes.name: Avocado Barter Adventure
episodes.overview: Wolf tries to find the perfect six-month anniversary gift for Honeybee. Meanwhile, Judy interviews Honeybee for the school newspaper and learns about her thrilling early years in Fresno.

episodes.name: Romantic Meat-Based Adventure
episodes.overview: Worried that she’s inherited Beef’s fear of romance, Judy forces her dad to get back out there by attending a meat auction and singles mixer in the hopes of bringing home a new love, and also maybe some sausages.

episodes.name: Curl Interrupted Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef enlists Judy to help coach his adult curling team. Meanwhile, Wolf tries to turn the family fishing boat into a sunset cruise for lovers.

episodes.name: Pride & Prejudance Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy asks her crush to the most romantic dance of the school year, not realizing he's got eyes for someone else. Meanwhile, Beef's Brother, Brian, comes up for a visit from Anchorage.

episodes.name: Period Piece Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy asks Alyson to help her with an exciting opportunity to lead an art project at school. Meanwhile, the local paper prints a story involving Beef, and the family investigates to discover the truth.

episodes.name: Keep Beef-lievin' Adventure
episodes.overview: When Moon begins to doubt the existence of Bigfoot, Beef enlists the family's help to get him believing again. Meanwhile, Honeybee gets a surprise visitor from Fresno.

episodes.name: Tusk in the Wind Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef and Wolf meet their hero, legendary mountain man, Tusk Johnson! Judy and the rest of the Tobin clan become addicted to '80s primetime soap "Dynasty".

episodes.name: Game of Snownes Adventure
episodes.overview: A blizzard threatens the Tobin family game night. Meanwhile, Beef makes a new friend in the woods.

episodes.name: My Fart Will Go On Adventure
episodes.overview: While the family prepares for Wolf and Honeybee's wedding, an unexpected guest RSVPs.

episodes.name: Brace/Off Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy embarks on a journey after getting some unexpected news from the dentist.

episodes.name: The Great Punkin' Adventure
episodes.overview: A punk band invites Ham to audition after hearing him scream. Meanwhile, Honeybee and Wolf get their first directing gig.

episodes.name: The Yawn of the Dead Adventure
episodes.overview: Moon, Judy and Ham try to survive Alaska's darkest and spookiest day of the year. Meanwhile, Wolf and Honeybee attempt to replace Beef's favorite shirt.

episodes.name: Wanted: Delmer Alive Adventure
episodes.overview: After Delmer suffers a concussion while eating soup, the Tobins tell their favorite stories about him in order to keep him awake and alive.

episodes.name: Beef's Craig Beef Adventure
episodes.overview: When Wolf discovers that Beef secretly wants a jet ski, he formulates a plan to get it; Ham bonds with a novelty singing fish toy.

episodes.name: Skidmark Holmes Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy's murder mystery party doesn't go exactly as planned; Alyson invites herself on a date with Beef.

episodes.name: Tasteful Noods Adventure
episodes.overview: Ham is assigned an after-school job at a restaurant as part of "Careers Week," and gets an unexpected surprise. Meanwhile, Moon develops a crush on an older woman.

episodes.name: Good Beef Hunting Adventure
episodes.overview: During Thanksgiving week, the Tobin kids and Honeybee take part in an old family tradition called The Beef Hunt. Meanwhile, Beef wrestles with his greatest fear.

episodes.name: From Tusk Til Dawn Adventure
episodes.overview: Former celebrity mountain man, Tusk Johnson, returns to Lone Moose with a big favor to ask of Beef and Wolf. Meanwhile, Honeybee enters a contest to win her own mall kiosk.

guest_stars.character: New Kids on the Dock Vocalist (voice)
guest_stars.name: Gary Anthony Williams

episodes.name: Dip The Halls Adventure
episodes.overview: When Jerry's Bigfoot costume gets stolen a few days before Christmas, Beef helps him track it down. The Tobin kids try to build an elaborate gingerbread village.

episodes.name: Dances With Wolfs Adventure
episodes.overview: Moon helps Wolf deal with their parents' divorce. Honeybee encounters Lone Moose's most famous City Councilperson, who happens to be an eagle.

episodes.name: Beef Mommas House Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef joins a local moms' group, while Moon and his friends build a Dread Sled. Meanwhile, the rest of the family digs into the investigation of Wolf and Honeybee's disappearing potholder.

episodes.name: Saved by the Spells Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy relaunches the Saved by the Spells, a legendary secret society. Meanwhile, Honeybee and Wolf have a surprising week, and Moon makes a new friend on his CB radio.

episodes.name: Stools Rush in Adventure
episodes.overview: The school is putting on a musical based on "The Perfect Storm," and Judy desperately wants to be one of the leads. Meanwhile, Moon tries to convince his family he's ready to stay home alone for the very first time.

episodes.name: You've Got Math Adventure
episodes.overview: Honeybee agrees to help Moon with his school problems, only to learn that something else is on his mind. Meanwhile, the rest of the family deals with a moose problem.

episodes.name: As Goldie As It Gets Adventure
episodes.overview: Ham befriends an older woman who loves to party. Meanwhile, Judy takes up pottery and is not great at it.

episodes.name: Dead Moon Walking Adventure
episodes.overview: After seeing something he shouldn't have, Moon incurs Debbie's wrath. Meanwhile, Beef is determined to save his favorite museum from being closed down.

episodes.name: Beef's in Toyland Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef struggles when the boat needs repairs and he can't fish for a whole week. Meanwhile, Wolf and Honeybee meet the best-looking man in Lone Moose.

episodes.name: Poetry of the Penals Adventure
episodes.overview: Wolf chaperones Ham and Judy on a school field trip to the abandoned Death Cliff Prison. Meanwhile, Beef accidentally agrees to compose a poem.

episodes.name: Say It Again, Ham Adventure
episodes.overview: With Crispin's help, Ham tries to re-create a more theatrical version of his coming out. Meanwhile, hoping to record their first true crime podcast, Wolf and Honeybee investigate a local cold case and are shocked by what they uncover.

episodes.name: Slide & Wet-judice Adventure
episodes.overview: A new indoor water park is opening in Lone Moose, and all of the Tobins want to go, except for Wolf, who's convinced that he's cursed to always lose his swim trunks in front of the entire town.

episodes.name: Papa Don't Fiend Adventure
episodes.overview: The Tobins spend Father's Day weekend at an RV park and uncover the identity of the Fiend of Family Land. Then, Moon meets a skunk, and Judy thinks she's found a new love.

episodes.name: A Knife to Remember Adventure
episodes.overview: Honeybee and Wolf discover an outback-themed restaurant they can't stop going to. Meanwhile, Beef confronts his fear of small talk.

episodes.name: Cillian Me Softly Adventure
episodes.overview: During Lone Moose's Disaster Day event, Wolf and Honeybee have their very first fight.

episodes.name: Autumn If You Got Em Adventure
episodes.overview: All the Tobins fall under the spell of the Fall Frenzy Dance.

episodes.name: Code Enough Said Adventure
episodes.overview: When the Tobins and some friends are trapped in the house for days by an ice storm, their cabin fever leads to the Trial of the Century.

episodes.name: Woodfellas Adventure
episodes.overview: The entire town of Lone Moose is determined to win the annual Cavalcade of Ships parade. Wolf uncovers a parade secret that could change everything.

episodes.name: Blood Actually Adventure
episodes.overview: It's Halloween! When Honeybee's plans to fly home to Fresno for her favorite holiday get ruined by a storm, she decides to bring her family traditions to Lone Moose, but faces a series of terrifying surprises.

episodes.name: Mall-mento Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef and Judy tell alternate versions of a wild day. The rest of the Tobins try to finish reading a challenging novel.

episodes.name: Dick, Rick, Groom Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef is recruited to pilot a super yacht owned by eccentric billionaire Dick Chateau. Wolf and Honeybee become convinced that a mysterious stranger is actually Wolf from the future.

episodes.name: Bee's All That Adventure
episodes.overview: Kima and her family host a very surprising visitor during Lone Moose's "lower-48" exchange student week. Ham fails to care for a cactus.

episodes.name: Xmas With the Skanks Adventure
episodes.overview: When a long lost family friend shows up at Lone Moose's White Elephant gift exchange, Beef is not pleased. Moon rescues a reindeer.

episodes.name: Arranger-ous Minds Adventure
episodes.overview: Moon and the Junior Janitors get involved with a teacher scandal. The rest of the family gets involved with a buncha crabs.

episodes.name: Enough Bed Adventure
episodes.overview: The kids must convince Beef to get a new mattress after his turns into a deadly trap. Honeybee and Wolf set out on a journey.

episodes.name: Sister Pact Too Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy and Honeybee encounter a strange group in the woods. The rest of the family has to save Beef from an arranged marriage.

episodes.name: Boy Meats World Adventure
episodes.overview: All of Lone Moose gets wrapped up in the Little Mr. Ketchikan Canned Sausage Gentleman Pageant competition, a pageant for boys with an unusual history.

episodes.name: Can't Hardly Date Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef drives Alyson to meet a man she met online. Wolf confronts his greatest fear: not being liked by a local bartender.

episodes.name: Great Bus of Choir Adventure
episodes.overview: Wolf and Honeybee's parenting skills are put to the test when an adult show choir crashes outside their home. Beef takes Moon on a surprise trip.

episodes.name: A Bear-tiful Find Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef, Wolf and Honeybee come upon a grizzly surprise when they go for coffee at Maude's diner. Ham and Moon go on a mission to reclaim a treasure.

episodes.name: Pa-Shank Redemption Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef goes to great lengths to avoid celebrating his birthday.

episodes.name: Rear Genius Adventure
episodes.overview: The citizens of Lone Moose celebrate the Rear Gifts Festival, an annual celebration of moose turds. Ham attempts to make a new friend his own age.

episodes.name: Barrel Be Blood Adventure
episodes.overview: When a hi-tech seafood vending machine shows up in Lone Moose and drives down the price of fish, Beef loses it. Judy and Kima become junior members of an all-women's smokejumper crew.

episodes.name: For Whom the Smell Tolls Adventure (1)
episodes.overview: Judy and Kima worry they won't find their perfect dates for prom. The rest of the family investigate a weird smell that's been wafting through town.

episodes.name: For Whom the Smell Tolls Adventure (2)
episodes.overview: It's a day of reckoning for Lone Moose, as Beef and a group of townspeople attempt to rescue all the prom-goers from a flood of rotten meat waste.

episodes.name: Bad Speecher Adventure
episodes.overview: Ham enlists his family for help in finding a speech for his Public Speaking Elective. Judy, Beef, and Honeybee pitch competing stories for Ham to select from and end up secretly drawing from Top Gun, Good Will Hunting, and The Matrix in the process.

episodes.name: Risky Beefness Adventure
episodes.overview: Beef has a one-night stand after a string of bad dates, but quickly becomes embarrassed when Greta Meatweep exposes their sexcapades in the poem column of the local newspaper. Moon becomes Jerry’s Bigfoot little-brother sidekick, and the local clown duo challenges them to a costume battle over the Lone Moose party turf.

episodes.name: Aunt Misbehavin' Adventure
episodes.overview: When Moon gets rejected by his crush for the Lil' Preppers Practice Prom, he goes off-grid for the night and sees a mysterious figure who is revealed to be the long-lost Aunt Dirt Tobin who has been in hiding in a bunker on the Tobin property since 1964. The Tobin family teaches Aunt Dirt all about modern life while Moon copes with his first bout of romantic rejection.

episodes.name: Ready Mayor Won Adventure
episodes.overview: Honeybee wins interim Lone Moose mayor over Wolf who, although upset, starts overstepping during Honeybee's one day term. The rest of the Tobins start capitalizing on their new family member's political power.

episodes.name: Cheese All That Adventure
episodes.overview: When Cheesecake gets evicted from his trailer but finds a dangerous job on a crabbing boat, Wolf and Honeybee struggle to get him a local job and to teach him interview skills. Meanwhile, Beef tries to help bring business to Carissa's failing coffee hut.

episodes.name: The Mighty Pucks Adventure
episodes.overview: As the Tobin family receives their annual oil dividend checks for living in Alaska, they all have different approaches on how to spend them. Honeybee and Wolf attempt to create a homemade gym in their guest house, and Beef, Moon, and Dirt scavenge junk yards looking for an extravagant object to buy. Meanwhile, Judy coaches the local hockey team in hopes of attracting their audience to her one-woman show protesting the dividends.

episodes.name: Judy Presents: The Staircake
episodes.overview: After Ham gets into a prestigious cake competition in New York, the family sets off on a bus road trip.

episodes.name: Bear of Beeftown Adventure
episodes.overview: When Beef is threatened by someone else potentially dating Carissa, he decides to fight a new bear from Fat Bear Week. Meanwhile, Ham takes Aunt Dirt to the gay bars around town, but she struggles to feel comfortable.

episodes.name: Idita-Ruth Adventure
episodes.overview: When the new librarian gets rid of the vandalized books, Moon and his friends retrieve them and set up a vandalized-book bookstore.

episodes.name: A Chug's Life Adventure
episodes.overview: When Judy and Ham realize that the school thinks they don't party, they set out with Aunt Dirt, Kima, Moon, and Crispin to find and party with Doug Delfino, a recently emancipated student.

episodes.name: High Expectations Adventure
episodes.overview: When Judy and Kima accidentally get high during a school field trip, they are sent on a mission to find treasure by a talking tub of cottage cheese named Beth. Meanwhile, Wolf's signature sandwich is removed from the menu at Lydia's sandwich shop.

episodes.name: Any Court In A Storm Adventure
episodes.overview: When a blizzard snows the Tobin family in, Beef struggles to avoid cabin fever by running the household like the Royal British Navy. But after a box of special candy is found half-eaten, Judy, Wolf, Moon, Ham, Honeybee, Jerry, and Mr. Golovkin turn on Beef, and everyone gets at each other's throats, threatening the sanity of the household.

episodes.name: You've Got Sail Adventure
episodes.overview: Wanting a chance at casually making out, Judy suddenly finds herself with three separate dates to handle simultaneously. Meanwhile, Beef goes to meet a friend he met online, only to find out that he's a cruise ship captain, and therefore a dire enemy.

episodes.name: Doctor? No! Adventure
episodes.overview: Out of concern for Beef's health, the kids push him to see a doctor. Meanwhile, a grave marked "Wife" pushes Honeybee, Judy, and Aunt Dirt into researching the corpse's life.

episodes.name: Fifty Worst Dates Adventure
episodes.overview: After Carissa’s friends tell Beef he needs to be more romantic, he takes her on a full day of consecutive dates. Honeybee and Judy plan their second annual opening of “The Tobin Family Pool”.

episodes.name: Excess Cabbage Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy investigates a mysterious cloaked figure who's buying up all her art. Beef, Wolf, Ham, and Moon grow a giant cabbage. Honeybee and Jerry compete to see who can keep foam fingers on the longest.

episodes.name: Welcome to Miami Adventure
episodes.overview: Coming off the heels of her break-up, Judy is taken on a wild adventure with Honeybee and Aunt Dirt.

episodes.name: Worst Drives Club Adventure
episodes.overview: Judy tries to learn to drive.

episodes.name: Look Who's Squawking Adventure
episodes.overview: When the eagle Moon is pet sitting escapes, he enlists Beef and Wolf to go searching for it.

episodes.name: Am I the Ice Hole? Adventure
episodes.overview: Honeybee and Beef bond on an ice fishing trip and try to find a compromise between quiet fishing and fun games.
